ces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，高中已經冇讀bio完全冇底，咩都唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"St. John 或者紅十字會既course唔貴, 可以考慮"},{"pid":"1a6cf3e872145203ea002b8ba8019c22cdcadf53","tid":1278340,"uid":267924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjMm6PE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjMm6PE.png&h=99a41d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855486ace31336a6fdd9d34713026991b57ed16e","tid":1278340,"uid":131247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"識first aid 點都唔係壞事。支持"},{"pid":"ba5cf4bf66bc8c84517e1d92b3d5e8404f4aa65d","tid":1278340,"uid":58069,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"a10ca8de9488e3710db0f6618db1dbaec8530461","tid":1278340,"uid":77220,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"想扮型溝女？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"上次發夢係警總正門果陣有位小姐訓低左，之後成班大叫first aid ,first aid同叫人散開。 跟住有幾位穿著便服既手足行埋去位小姐隔離問佢咩事，我身邊就有人大叫話冇急救知識既唔好過去。呢個時候其中一位係小姐隔離既手足大叫：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢度全部都係醫生！！</span> . 果刻係小弟見過最撚型既一刻。"},{"pid":"1bf3b568f4458ea3f5aeb16c71bfe10e0dbb1403","tid":1278340,"uid":94718,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"考咗紅十字會或 St John 先。紅十字會有 Online Lecture，再上兩日包紥；St John 就上足四個 Full day，再考試。<br />\n<br />\n其實非常皮毛，有心學可以再入隊爭取實習機會。學急救，實有用。現場有專業醫護，但普通去和理非遊行幫手都好。<br />\n<br />\n利申：有紅會cert，都想幫手處理輕傷"},{"pid":"ff32ce45f35cfc0c694f85a5eed8ad2a513a3071","tid":1278340,"uid":162344,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"真心既，唔係講玩<br />\n交返比義務醫生同義務護士<br />\n以免越幫越忙<br />\n<br />\n利申：護狗"},{"pid":"65344637410affe5c2c7ab4a59edbc920246b3de","tid":1278340,"uid":257415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"red cross同st john都有course上"},{"pid":"d72fc9f67de86f06a1b4e7e23f9fdbb837e45e95","tid":1278340,"uid":242851,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"唔係有急救牌就做到 急救牌哩啲皮毛野黎"},{"pid":"b0115cbb40d631519abc76c80231ff3eed65de17","tid":1278340,"uid":162344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff32ce45f35cfc0c694f85a5eed8ad2a513a3071","tid":1278340,"uid":162344,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"真心既，唔係講玩<br />\n交返比義務醫生同義務護士<br />\n以免越幫越忙<br />\n<br />\n利申：護狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"唔一定參與急救行列至叫幫手<br />\n讓路同聯絡已經係最大嘅幫忙"},{"pid":"858469071f3074e2af732d8b88c45898d24e4534","tid":1278340,"uid":58069,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"自己知道自己咩春都唔識，我唔會考完個牌就覺得自己好勁妄下判斷。不過我相信考完個牌，起碼會有少少認識，現場真係出事果陣而咁岩冇相關人士既時候可以阻止人地做d危害傷者既事。"},{"pid":"78216bd0bad60957df7edf5f91a249abd52b9cb7","tid":1278340,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"唔係考張cert就得<br />\n唔識搓唔好亂鳩咁搓"},{"pid":"87299c79dd3e543b62bbcb8984e6b8026fa6f0b2","tid":1278340,"uid":63865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"啱啱都考左紅十字first aid，上堂教嘅真係好皮毛，真係for你應付考試，雖然臨場一定好大分別，但都叫多叮叮急救知識，我都好想幫到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d9a695463c3f6a23c7769e857697fd2b37caea","tid":1278340,"uid":249939,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"我都有St John急救牌<br />\n但發夢個陣有人叫First Aid我都真係唔敢去<br />\n如果係普通輕傷個啲都叫識點做<br />\n但去到好似612個啲咁我真係唔識點做"}]}